thread.title_full: Muscle Meals Direct reviewed by Caeleb Doughty

author: Caeleb Doughty
title: Caeleb Doughty
text:
As a full time worker and part time Personal Trainer, for years I would not only struggle to eat healthy, but also to eat more frequently. And not only do i feel better, but I am personally able to perform better in the gym, and at Kung fu.
My goal was to gain lean muscle and I have done so very easily thanks to muscle meals direct !
And of course my intense training ;)
Thanks guys!
